# OBJECT::CLEAR_PICKUP_REWARD_TYPE_SUPPRESSION

## Summary
Clears a designated suppression pickup flag

## Parameters
* **PICKUP_REWARD_TYPE** pickupFlag: Flag you would like to clear (refer to enum PICKUP_REWARD_TYPE )
